 +A  !!= * @CODE@  adjective
 +Adp  !!= * @CODE@  adposition
 +Adv  !!= * @CODE@  adverb
 +CS  !!= * @CODE@  subordinating conjunction
 +CC  !!= * @CODE@  coordinating conjunction
 +Interj  !!= * @CODE@  interjection
 +N     !!= * @CODE@  noun
 +Pcle  !!= * @CODE@  particle
 +Po    !!= * @CODE@  postposition
 +Pr    !!= * @CODE@  preposition
 +Pron  !!= * @CODE@  pronoun
 +Qnt   !!= * @CODE@  quantifier
 +V     !!= * @CODE@  verb
 +Num   !!= * @CODE@  numeral

+AdA         !!= * @CODE@  Ad-adjective
+Bahuv	     !!= * @CODE@  Bahuvrihi
